Package: libevemu1
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Interface to kernel input events
 A programmatic API to access the kernel input event devices. The original and
 intended purpose is for supporting multi-touch input, especially with regard
 to the Linux touch and gesture stack.
